{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dodgeball Blast</strong> is an action-packed boss rush game where your dodgeball skills will be put to the ultimate test! Face off against 10 wild and wacky bosses, each with their own unique abilities and personalities, as you fight your way to becoming the ultimate Dodgeball Master!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>10 Unique Bosses \u2013 Dodge, Throw, Survive!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261250/extras/DBB_some_bosses.jpg?t=1740530543\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face off against a <strong>wild lineup of over-the-top bosses</strong>, each with their own crazy attacks and unpredictable dodgeball skills. From a <strong>Bigfoot brawler on the wing of a plane</strong> to a <strong>Kung Fu Dodgeball Master</strong>, every fight is a ridiculous showdown!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Minigames \u2013 More Than Just Dodgeball!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261250/extras/dbb_minigame.jpg?t=1740530543\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take a break from the chaos with <strong>wacky minigames</strong> that test your reflexes, aim, and dodging prowess. Can you master the art of extreme dodgeball trick shots?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unlockable Abilities \u2013 Power Up Your Game!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261250/extras/dbb_abilities.jpg?t=1740530543\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you progress, <strong>earn and equip new abilities</strong> to enhance your dodgeball domination. Super-speed dodges, power throws, and other insane skills will change how you take on the competition!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Local 2-Player Versus Mode \u2013 Settle the Score!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261250/extras/dbb_2player.jpg?t=1740530543\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge a friend in <strong>head-to-head dodgeball battles</strong>! Outplay, outlast, and out-dodge your opponent\u2014because in dodgeball, only the craftiest player walks away victorious!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3261250?t=1740530543","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261250/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740530543","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261250/281f1356948f09f004c79786cbc58535b6bf9dbf/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740530543","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261250/281f1356948f09f004c79786cbc58535b6bf9dbf/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740530543","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dodgeball Blast</strong> is an action-packed boss rush game where your dodgeball skills will be put to the ultimate test! Face off against 10 wild and wacky bosses, each with their own unique abilities and personalities, as you fight your way to becoming the ultimate Dodgeball Master!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>10 Unique Bosses \u2013 Dodge, Throw, Survive!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a